    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288310/extras/862b80813d40611f57bbb4dbd8bd07c3.avif?t=1724981750\" width=300 height=150 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288310/extras/67ff8a3c6845ccf46cf8476818637f18.avif?t=1724981750\" width=300 height=79 /></span><br>Five nights at Tinky's is a trial and error game that is inspired by fnaf,<br>where you play as someone who is low on money and searches for a quick way to make money,<br>after finding a nightguard job that lasts 5 nights at the &quot;Tinkys Lasagne Place&quot; for alot of money you instantly applied for it and ofcourse they chose you.<br>Its gonna be your first night in &quot;Tinkys Lasagne Place&quot; and maybe its your last...<br>Can you survive the 5 nights?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288310/extras/b2106690a6695c74fcb08849428fc8e4.avif?t=1724981750\" width=300 height=83 /></span><br>Survive in a small room with 1 main door to a hallway, 1 vent infront of you and 1 vent behind you.<br>You can control your vent doors by using your tablet you received and close the doors infront of you by using their buttons.<br>Check the doors by using the light switch or the flashlight but do not flash the wrong animatronics!<br>Keep the monsters out of your room and do not let them get inside!<br>Explore after each night to find clues on what happened to this place.<br><br><strong>Five nights at Tinky's Includes:</strong><br>-A storymode with multiple choice endings.<br><br>-Five Nights that get harder the further you progress.<br><br>-One extra night for the challenge.<br><br>-Four Monsters with unique abilities and different weaknesses. | Do not let them get you.<br><br>-Custom Nights once you beat the main game. | Set the monsters on the level you like.<br><br>-Endless Nights once you beat the main game with a steam leaderboard. | Showoff in the public steam leaderboard.<br><br>-Customizable Office. | Random item drops that are tradeable and marketable.<br><br>-Achivements not too hard and not too easy.<br><br>-Goofy phonecalls. | They are really goofy.<br><br>-Trading Cards and Emotes depend on the sales of the game.<br><br><i>This game contains jumpscares. ( They aren't that scary :3 )</i>",
